vote.title: Authorize the first of two twelve-month renewal options to the service contract with Citizens Development Center dba U&I, and f/d/b/a Achieve, to provide a senior employment program for the period September 10, 2022 through September 9, 2023 - Not to exceed $102,600.00, from $82,270.00 to $184,870.00 - Financing:  General Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
